Race.SpecificTitle: Sub-Road Dist. Number One of Road Dist. Number Two -- 5 Mills - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Sub-Road District Number One of Road District Number Two Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Sub-Road District Number One of Road District Number Two of St. Helena Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), be authorized to levy a special tax of five (5) mills on all property subject to taxation within the District (an estimated $9,400 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purpose of maintaining and keeping in repair the public roads, highways and bridges in the District?
